\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {21}{\ignorespaces Final sample after the fabrication process. The four contacts pads are visible in the corners. It is clearly visible that the lines connecting the contact pads are below the green isolation layer. The CPW flows over the isolation layer, indicating a successful fabrication process.\relax }}{32}{figure.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{final_sample}{{21}{32}{Final sample after the fabrication process. The four contacts pads are visible in the corners. It is clearly visible that the lines connecting the contact pads are below the green isolation layer. The CPW flows over the isolation layer, indicating a successful fabrication process.\relax }{figure.caption.21}{}}
